---
title: Quick Irish-Style Beyond Meat® Stew with Garlic Crostini
description: In this hearty twist on a classic stew, we've swapped in quick-cooking Beyond Meat® so your meal will be on the table in less than 40 minutes. Don't forget to wipe the bowl clean with a slice of garlic crostini!
